<article class="config-card config-card-soft">
  <div class="section-head">
    <div>
      <p class="panel-kicker">IA e midia</p>
      <h3>Configuracao de provider e modelo</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="config-actions">
      <button id="enrichmentSave" type="button">Salvar configuracoes</button>
      <button id="enrichmentLoadModels" type="button">Carregar modelos</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="config-module-intro">
    <strong>Modelo, escopo e politica de processamento</strong>
    <p>Defina provider, credenciais, batch e o que deve ser gerado em cada documento antes de iniciar a fila.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="form-grid">
    <label>
      <span>Provider</span>
      <select id="enrichmentProvider">
        <option value="disabled">Desativado</option>
        <option value="local">IA local</option>
        <option value="cloud">API em nuvem</option>
      </select>
    </label>
    <label>
      <span>Modelo</span>
      <input id="enrichmentModel" type="text" list="enrichmentModelOptions" placeholder="ex: qwen2.5, llama3.1, gpt-4o-mini" />
      <datalist id="enrichmentModelOptions"></datalist>
    </label>
    <label>
      <span>Base URL</span>
      <input id="enrichmentBaseUrl" type="text" placeholder="Ollama: http://127.0.0.1:11434/api ou /v1" />
    </label>
    <label>
      <span>API key</span>
      <input id="enrichmentApiKey" type="text" placeholder="Opcional para IA local" />
    </label>
    <label>
      <span>Lote por execucao</span>
      <select id="enrichmentBatchLimit">
        <option value="3">3</option>
        <option value="5" selected>5</option>
        <option value="10">10</option>
        <option value="20">20</option>
      </select>
    </label>
    <label>
      <span>Modo do processo</span>
      <select id="enrichmentProcessMode">
        <option value="both" selected>Resumo e miniaturas</option>
        <option value="summary_only">Somente resumo</option>
        <option value="images_only">Somente miniaturas</option>
      </select>
    </label>
    <label>
      <span>Miniaturas por documento</span>
      <select id="enrichmentPreviewImageCount">
        <option value="1" selected>1</option>
        <option value="2">2</option>
        <option value="3">3</option>
        <option value="4">4</option>
        <option value="5">5</option>
      </select>
    </label>
    <label>
      <span>Qualidade das imagens</span>
      <select id="enrichmentPreviewImageQuality">
        <option value="low">Baixa</option>
        <option value="balanced" selected>Balanceada</option>
        <option value="high">Alta</option>
      </select>
    </label>
  </div>

  <div class="button-row">
    <label class="toggle-line strong-line">
      <input id="enrichmentSummaryEnabled" type="checkbox" checked />
      <span>Gerar resumos trabalhados para os documentos</span>
    </label>
    <label class="toggle-line strong-line">
      <input id="enrichmentPreviewImagesEnabled" type="checkbox" />
      <span>Gerar miniaturas leves da primeira pagina</span>
    </label>
    <label class="toggle-line strong-line">
      <input id="enrichmentOverwriteSummary" type="checkbox" />
      <span>Refazer resumos mesmo quando o documento ja tiver resumo</span>
    </label>
    <label class="toggle-line strong-line">
      <input id="enrichmentOverwritePreviewImages" type="checkbox" />
      <span>Refazer miniaturas mesmo quando o documento ja tiver imagens</span>
    </label>
  </div>

  <p class="config-note">Para Ollama, use <strong>`http://127.0.0.1:11434/api`</strong> para API nativa ou <strong>`http://127.0.0.1:11434/v1`</strong> para compatibilidade OpenAI.</p>
</article>
